window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>\"Look me in my eyes. If you really think I did this shit, then leave. Don’t walk down that aisle. I’ll handle this on my own.\" Dom</p> <p>“I’m doing this for my family and our reputation not for you.” Zoree<br> <br> At a young age, Dom Kincaid thought he had met the girl of his dreams, Zoree Boudreaux. However, fate had other plans. Forced apart, their lives travel down different path until those paths cross years later.<br> <br> Forced together out of necessity, the two have to perpetuate the ultimate commitment, marriage.<br> <br> Will the arrangement give the two a second chance at love? Or will the past that separated them keep them apart?<br> <br> To protect their families, the arrangement began but the true question is how will it end…</p>"; 
